title: REPLAY w/ Gwyneth Paltrow
itunes:title: REPLAY w/ Gwyneth Paltrow
description:
Original Air Date: June 23, 2021


PANTS with Kate Moennig and Leisha Hailey

Produced by Melisa D. Monts and Diamond MPrint Productions

 

This week the duo are chatting with Kate’s cousin Gwyneth Paltrow! They share stories from their childhood and answer listener questions about getting over exes, not liking your friend’s partner, and their most spontaneous activities.

 

Follow us on Twitter @ThePantsPod

Follow us on Instagram @ThePantsPod

Email us: pantspodcast@yahoo.com

Music: Carol Parra @csssuxxx

Artwork: Lovefoxxx
